1950.; (box)"Breaking the Sound Barrier," 1952.; (box)"Hobson's Choice,"
1954.; (box)"Summertime," 1955.; (box)"The Bridge on the River Kwai," 1957.;
(box)"Lawrence of Arabia," 1962.; (box)"Dr. Zhivago," 1965.; (box)"Ryan's
Daughter," 1970.; (box)"A Passage to India," 1984.; Source: Associated Press  </TEXT>
